N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1273.4 - Presence of at least two approved fire extinguishers required

State Regulations

During fuel handling operations in connection with any
aircraft at the air terminal, at least two 20 pound or larger dry chemical fire
extinguishers shall be immediately available for use in connection
